                   managelogs installation instructions
                   ------------------------------------


* Edit the Makefile file in the base directory and modify the
  'modifiable' parameters according to your environment.

* Run 'make'

* 'make install' will copy :
		- the managelogs executable to <apache-path>/bin
		- the logmanager.h include file to <apache-path>/include
		- the logmanager.a library to <apache-path>/lib

A better build system (using autoconf) is planned (see the TODO file).

